{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"a100000000000001","type":"text","x":-1100,"y":-720,"width":2200,"height":120,"color":"1","text":"# Agents 工作流：主会话调度 + 6 agent + 默认流水线 + Plan-first + 并行模板\n\n**调度权必须留主会话**（ADR-003），`team-leader` 不再被 spawn；subagent 嵌套 spawn 仅用于自我加速（ADR-037）。"},
		{"id":"u100000000000001","type":"text","x":-260,"y":-560,"width":520,"height":120,"color":"3","text":"## 主会话（team-leader 内嵌）\n\n需求拆解 / 任务分配 / 并行编排 / 质量卡点 / 最终交付\n\n**不写代码 / 不写文档 / 不做审查**"},
		{"id":"r200000000000001","type":"text","x":-1080,"y":-380,"width":300,"height":160,"color":"6","text":"## architect\nopus / plan\n\n仅新模块 / 继承体系 / 跨模块依赖；**不写实现代码**，出方案后交回主会话"},
		{"id":"r200000000000002","type":"text","x":-760,"y":-380,"width":300,"height":160,"color":"5","text":"## runtime-coder\nsonnet / auto\n\n框架核心 + 业务 C# 代码"},
		{"id":"r200000000000003","type":"text","x":-440,"y":-380,"width":300,"height":160,"color":"5","text":"## editor-coder\nsonnet / auto\n\nInspector / EditorWindow / Pipify 数据流水线"},
		{"id":"r200000000000004","type":"text","x":-120,"y":-380,"width":300,"height":160,"color":"4","text":"## code-reviewer\nsonnet / plan\n\n静态审查：逻辑 + 风格 + 架构 + 安全 + 性能 + 文档同步\n仅修确定性缺陷"},
		{"id":"r200000000000005","type":"text","x":200,"y":-380,"width":300,"height":160,"color":"4","text":"## qa-reviewer\nsonnet / plan\n\n三步运行时验证：编译 + Inspector + Play Mode `[PASS]`/`[FAIL]`\n仅修测试 / trivial"},
		{"id":"r200000000000006","type":"text","x":520,"y":-380,"width":300,"height":160,"color":"2","text":"## doc-writer\nsonnet / auto\n\n`Assets/Framework/Docs/` 同步 + INDEX.md；仅写文档"},
		{"id":"p300000000000001","type":"group","x":-1100,"y":-160,"width":2200,"height":260,"label":"默认流水线（轻量快速通道可叠加跳过 reviewer/doc-writer）","color":"5"},
		{"id":"p310000000000001","type":"text","x":-1080,"y":-110,"width":300,"height":80,"color":"5","text":"### 1. 需求 → 主会话拆解"},
		{"id":"p310000000000002","type":"text","x":-760,"y":-110,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"6","text":"### 2. （可选）architect 出方案"},
		{"id":"p310000000000003","type":"text","x":-480,"y":-110,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"5","text":"### 3. coder 实现\nruntime / editor"},
		{"id":"p310000000000004","type":"text","x":-200,"y":-110,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"4","text":"### 4. code-reviewer\n静态审查"},
		{"id":"p310000000000005","type":"text","x":80,"y":-110,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"4","text":"### 5. qa-reviewer\n运行时验证"},
		{"id":"p310000000000006","type":"text","x":360,"y":-110,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"2","text":"### 6. doc-writer\n文档同步"},
		{"id":"p310000000000007","type":"text","x":640,"y":-110,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"3","text":"### 7. 主会话验收 → 交付"},
		{"id":"p320000000000001","type":"text","x":-1080,"y":-10,"width":2160,"height":80,"color":"5","text":"**轻量快速通道**：① 跳 code-reviewer → 直接 qa（低风险 / 纯 UI 位置-大小 / 文案 / 显而易见小 bug）；② 跳 doc-writer（不冲击对外接口）。**多模块 / 新功能 / 架构变更必走完整流程**。"},
		{"id":"f400000000000001","type":"group","x":-1100,"y":140,"width":2200,"height":220,"label":"Plan-first 模式（命中即必走 ExitPlanMode）","color":"1"},
		{"id":"f410000000000001","type":"text","x":-1080,"y":190,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"1","text":"### 触发条件\n\n- 跨模块（≥2）\n- 新增 / 重构 Component / Manager\n- 新增 / 改 public API / Inspector 字段\n- ≥3 文件 / diff > 200 行\n- HybridCLR / Procedure / Hotfix\n- 新建 / 推翻 ADR"},
		{"id":"f410000000000002","type":"text","x":-720,"y":190,"width":520,"height":140,"color":"1","text":"### Plan 必备结构\n\n顶部 **【知识库前置匹配】** 节：命中条目 / 强制术语 / 反模式 / 冲突解决；如无命中显式标注\n\n→ 用户 ExitPlanMode 通过后才能派活"},
		{"id":"f410000000000003","type":"text","x":-180,"y":190,"width":1260,"height":140,"color":"1","text":"### 跳过即红线\n\n命中触发条件却跳过 ExitPlanMode 直接派活 = 「质量类红线」违反；缺顶部「知识库前置匹配」节同样视为违反。详 `team-leader.md`「Plan-first 模式」节 + ADR-034 (architect 强制前置)。"},
		{"id":"t500000000000001","type":"group","x":-1100,"y":400,"width":2200,"height":520,"label":"四大并行模板（A / B / C / D）—— 详 PAT-75","color":"4"},
		{"id":"t510000000000001","type":"text","x":-1080,"y":450,"width":520,"height":200,"color":"4","text":"## 模板 A：code-reviewer 双路并行\n\n触发：单次 diff > 100 行\n\n动作：拆\"逻辑路\"+\"风格/架构路\"两个 reviewer 并行，结果汇合再交 qa\n\nADR-035 / PAT-08"},
		{"id":"t510000000000002","type":"text","x":-540,"y":450,"width":520,"height":200,"color":"4","text":"## 模板 B：多 coder worktree 并行\n\n触发：≥2 coder 同任务并行\n\n动作：每 coder 单独 git worktree（superpowers:using-git-worktrees）；\"两实例不得同改一文件\"红线\n\nADR-036"},
		{"id":"t510000000000003","type":"text","x":0,"y":450,"width":520,"height":200,"color":"4","text":"## 模板 C：architect-first 并行\n\n触发：跨模块 / 新建 Manager / 继承体系\n\n动作：先 architect 出方案，方案中拆出独立子任务后再派多 coder\n\n**禁跳 architect 直接派 coder**（ADR-034）"},
		{"id":"t510000000000004","type":"text","x":540,"y":450,"width":520,"height":200,"color":"4","text":"## 模板 D：UnityMCP batch_execute\n\n触发：多次串行 UnityMCP 调用\n\n动作：用 `batch_execute` 包装；多次单调用 = 红线（PAT-76）"},
		{"id":"t520000000000001","type":"text","x":-1080,"y":680,"width":2160,"height":120,"color":"4","text":"## 派发规约（superpowers:dispatching-parallel-agents 四步法）\n\n1. 列出本轮所有可并行 agent；2. 每个 agent prompt 顶部写「严禁触碰文件清单」；3. 单 message 多 Agent 并发 spawn；4. 收口 diff 比对清单防越权（详 `feedback_agent_scope_discipline`）"},
		{"id":"t520000000000002","type":"text","x":-1080,"y":820,"width":2160,"height":80,"color":"4","text":"**Vault 前置查询**（PAT-82）：所有 agent 接活前必先 grep / search Vault；产出顶部必有「知识库前置匹配」节；命中条目与实现冲突需说明遵循 / 推翻 / 部分违反关系"}
	],
